{
  "text": "In patients with PBNO and minor symptoms, watchful waiting may be recommended. If therapy is necessary, alpha blockers are the first-line treatment. The next treatment possibility is a transurethral incision of the bladder neck [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "25705234"
